- Recent user access refers to user interactions within the last 7 days; 
- Recent report activities refer to reports created or updated within the last 7 days; 
- Economic indicators are various metrics used to evaluate a country's economic performance, such as GDP, inflation rate, or unemployment rate.

sql:
SELECT c.country_name
FROM countries c
JOIN hdi_data h ON c.country_id = h.country_id
WHERE h.hdi_value = (
    SELECT MAX(hdi_value) FROM hdi_data
);
